{"tid":675401,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"依家既酒樓侍應真係無禮貌，連醫生都夠膽鬧","createTime":"2018-05-23T13:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T07:46:36.000Z","uid":1426,"like":12,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a59a750250e9a12630c9c100cdb6fcb2f38227c7","tid":675401,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"今天我陪朋友同埋佢屋企人去酒樓飲茶<br />\n點知見到個酒樓侍應態度勁差<br />\n成個人黑口黑面，謂野又大聲<br />\n咁我個朋友咪同佢個仔講<br />\n「你依家唔讀書，第時就好似呢個叔叔咁做侍應架啦。」<br />\n點知個侍應聽到之後，<br />\n唔知係咪佢太過自卑，竟然勁大聲喝我朋友<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/funk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Ffunk.gif&h=1334bd1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫佢唔好狗眼看人低<br />\n我朋友見到佢發脾氣<br />\n咪解釋自己只係教仔，唔係睇佢唔起<br />\n點知佢仲起度發神經<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_42.gif&h=2832b497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後我話比個侍應聽，我個朋友係醫生<br />\n佢無父蔭，完全靠自己本事做到呢份高尚既職業<br />\n叫佢尊重一下我朋友<br />\n但係佢仲起度亂鬧人<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_42.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_42.gif&h=2832b497&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後要酒樓經理出黎調停先解決陣事<br />\n<br />\n你地話依家香港地服務業發生咩事，連醫生都敢鬧<br />\n點解佢地既服務態度可以差到咁<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/images/smilies/default/smile_13.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_13.gif&h=ae0ff146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"984436152f253cec79c4d10a8d75cb837e99ed29","tid":675401,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b546f85872270e980a4fe9592daaaded18b13f","tid":675401,"uid":134171,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"屌on9<br />\ncop